TITLE: Extracting Token Data and Refresh Token Expiration
DESCRIPTION: After successful validation, extracts access token, expiry time, and refresh token from the response. Additionally, checks for 'refresh_expires_in' to determine refresh token lifespan. This facilitates token management and session expiration handling.
SOURCE: https://github.com/pilcrowonpaper/arctic/blob/main/docs/pages/providers/bungie.md#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: TypeScript
CODE:
```
const tokens = await bungie.validateAuthorizationCode(code);
const accessToken = tokens.accessToken();
const accessTokenExpiresAt = tokens.accessTokenExpiresAt();
const refreshToken = tokens.refreshToken();

// Get refresh token expiration in seconds
if ("refresh_expires_in" in tokens.data && typeof tokens.data.refresh_expires_in === "number") {
	const refreshTokenExpiresIn = tokens.data.refresh_expires_in;
}
```

